C%20due%20on%20January%2022.%20Sources%20said%20PM%20Modi%20is%20strictly%20following%20%26quot%3BYam%20rules%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20rituals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2011-day%20code%20includes%20penance%20and%20purifying%20the%20mind%20and%20body%20with%20meditation%20and%20special%20%26quot%3Bsatvik%26quot%3B%20diet%20that%20bars%20onion%2C%20garlic%20and%20several%20other%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20sleeping%20on%20the%20floor%20with%20only%20a%20blanket%20and%20has%20been%20only%20drinking%20coconut%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rituals%20for%20the%20temple%20consecration%20started%20from%20January%2012.%20On%20January%2022%2C%20PM%20Modi%20will%20perform%20the%20puja%20for%20the%20%26quot%3BPran%20Pratistha'%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20A%20team%20of%20priests%20led%20by%20Lakshmikant%20Dixit%20will%20perform%20the%20main%20rituals%20of%20the%20Pran%20Prathistha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPran%20Pratistha'%20means%20imbibing%20the%20idol%20with%20divine%20consciousness%20and%20is%20a%20must%20for%20every%20idol%20that%20is%20worshipped%20in%20a%20temple.%20The%20auspicious%20time%20for%20it%20is%2012.30%20pm%20on%20January%2022%2C%20the%20temple%20committee%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Lalla%20idol%20--%20a%20depiction%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20at%20the%20age%20of%20five%20years%20in%20black%20stone%2C%20sculpted%20by%20Mysuru-based%20sculptor%20Arun%20Yogiraj%20--%20was%20carried%20to%20the%20temple%20last%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20placed%20in%20the%20sanctorum%20sanctorum%20following%20a%20special%20puja%20ceremony.%20The%20formal%20installation%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20held%20today%2C%20Shri%20Ram%20Mandir%20Construction%20Committee%20chairperson%20Nripendra%20Mishra%20has%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consecration%20will%20be%20witnessed%20by%20over%2011%2C000%20guests%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20abroad%20who%20have%20been%20specially%20invited%20by%20the%20t