ning%20the%20city%20of%20656%2C300%20offers%20some%20perks%20of%20the%20quiet%20life%20as%20well%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20key%20factor%20is%20affordability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20price%20is%20right%20in%20Las%20Vegas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaving-california-moving-to-las-vegas-living-in-seattle-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edriving%20many%20people%20out%20of%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20the%20wealthiest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20quite%20some%20time%20the%20people%20that%20were%20leaving%20California%20were%20lower-income%20individuals%2C%20but%20more%20recently%2C%20those%20who%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-las-wealthy-are-moving-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Every%20wealthy%20are%20leaving%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20tax%20challenges%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20regulation%2C%26quot%3B%20chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20Coldwell%20Banker%20Premier%20Realty%20Bob%20Hamrick%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BLas%20Vegas%20has%20been%20the%20benefactor%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Too%2C%2031%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20people%20who%20left%20California%20for%20Nevada.%20Too%2C%20an%20artist%20and%20student%2C%20was%20living%20in%20San%20Francisco%20in%20a%20home%20his%20family%20owned%20when%20he%20realized%20that%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20wasn't%20worth%20it%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20family%20sold%20the%20three-bedroom%20duplex%20in%20San%20Francisco%20for%20around%20%241.1%20million%20and%20purchased%20a%20three-bedroom%20house%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20for%20between%20%24400%2C000%20and%20%24500%2C000%2C%20Too%20said.%20The%20Vegas%20home%20is%20three%20times%20the%20size%20of%20the%20one%20in%20San%20Francisco%20and%20has%20a%20backyard%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20holding%20two%20dogs%20inside%20of%20his%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a83d5d43bb77284b9de750%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EToo%20moved%20from%20San%20Francisco%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20and%20got%20a%20bigger%20place%20for%20half%20the%20price.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Michael%20Too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReal%20estate%20isn't%20the%20only%20thing%20that's%20cheaper.%20Too%20said%20groceries%2C%20gas%2C%20and%20even%20movie%20tickets%20are%20less%20pricey%20in%20Las%20Vegas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20median%20home%20price%20of%20%24435%2C900%2C%20according%20to%20Redfin%2C%20Nevada%20homes%20are%20slightly%20above%20the%20national%20median%20of%20%24408%2C537.%20But%20they're%20still%20way%20cheaper%20than%20homes%20in%20neighboring%20California%2C%20where%20the%20median%20home%20price%20is%20%24793%2C400.%20And%20with%20no%20state%20income%20tax%20in%20Nevada%2C%20that%20money%20saved%20goes%20much%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIncome%20tax%20is%20zero%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Arevalo%20said%2C%20which%20isn't%20the%20case%20in%20California.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20all%20they%20really%20care%20about%20is%20their%20bottom%20dollar%20in%20their%20pocket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThere's%20always%20things%20to%20do%20in%20Las%20Vegas%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20Las%20Vegas's%20casinos%20are%20open%2024%2F7%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20the%20only%20perk%20of%20the%20town.%20Surrounding%20the%20desert%20city%20is%20a%20vast%20landscape%20brimming%20with%20outdoor%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20definitely%20a%20lot%20of%20outdoors%2C%20and%20that's%20something%20I%20started%20getting%20more%20into%20when%20I%20moved%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Too%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20other%20places%20I've%20lived%2C%20it's%20a%20lot%20further%20of%20a%20drive.%20Here%20you%20can%20get%20out%20to%20the%20publ