content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18164057%2Fjustice-6983006_1280.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%20write%20this%20piece%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%20and%20a%20grave%20sense%20of%20responsibility.%20This%20is%20because%20I%20am%20writing%20about%20the%20%3Cem%3ESentinel%20on%20the%20Qui%20Vive%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20phrase%20etched%20in%20Indian%20jurisprudence%20by%20Justice%20Patanjali%20Sastry%20in%20his%20judgment%20in%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmain.sci.gov.in%2Fjonew%2Fjudis%2F1138.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EState%20of%20Madras%20v.%20VG%20Row%2C%20Union%20of%20India%20%26amp%3B%20State%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0in%20the%20following%20paragraph%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20is%20sometimes%20overlooked%2C%20that%20our%20Constitution%20contains%20express%20provisions%20for%20judicial%20review%20of%20legislation%20as%20to%20its%20conformity%20with%20the%20Constitution%2C%20unlike%20as%20in%20America%20where%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20assumed%20extensive%20powers%20of%20reviewing%20legislative%20acts%20undercover%20of%20the%20widely%20interpreted%20%E2%80%9Cdue%20process%E2%80%9D%20clause%20in%20the%20Fifth%20and%20Fourteenth%20Amendments.%20If%20then%2C%20the%20courts%20in%20this%20country%20face%20up%20to%20such%20important%20and%20none%20too%20easy%20task%2C%20it%20is%20not%20out%20of%20any%20desire%20to%20tilt%20at%20legislative%20authority%20in%20a%20crusader%E2%80%99s%20spirit%2C%20but%20in%20the%20discharge%20of%20a%20duty%20plainly%20laid%20upon%20them%20by%20the%20Constitution.%20This%20is%20especially%20true%20as%20regards%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfundamental%20rights%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20to%20which%20this%20court%20has%20been%20given%20the%20role%20of%20Sentinel%20on%20the%20Qui%20Vive.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20immediate%20cause%20of%20concern%20arises%20from%20the%20recent%20public%20utterances%20by%20two%20of%20the%20seniormost%20members%20of%20the%20highest%20judiciary%20in%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStandards%20of%20judicial%20conduct%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20these%20public%20utterances%20bring%20to%20mind%20is%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.main.sci.gov.in%2Fpdf%2FNotice%2F02112020_090821.pdf%5C%22%3ERestatement%20of%20Values%20of%20Judicial%20Life%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20adopted%20by%20a%20Full%20Court%20Meeting%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20on%20May%2007%2C%201997.%20This%20%E2%80%9Crestatement%E2%80%9D%20was%20ratified%20and%20adopted%20by%20the%20Indian%20judiciary%20in%20the%20Chief%20Justices%E2%80%99%20Conference%201999.%20All%20the%20high%20courts%20in%20the%20country%20also%20adopted%20the%20same%20in%20their%20respective%20Full%20Court%20Meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Crestatement%E2%80%9D%20ends%20with%20the%20following%20sentence%3A%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20only%20the%20%E2%80%9CRestatement%20of%20the%20Values%20of%20Judicial%20Life%E2%80%9D%20and%20are%20not%20meant%20to%20be%20exhaustive%20but%20illustrative%20of%20what%20is%20expected%20of%20a%20Judge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20in%20case%20a%201997%20%E2%80%9Crestatement%E2%80%9D%20is%20considered%20out%20of%20date%20(though%20there%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20have%20been%20any%20later%20document%20for%20Indian%20judiciary)%20there%20is%20a%20later%20document%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unodc.org%2Fpdf%2Fcrime%2Fcorruption%2Fjudicial_group%2FBangalore_principles.pdf%5C%22%3EThe%20Bangalore%20Principles%20of%20Judicial%20Conduct%202002%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0adopted%20by%20the%20Judicial%20Group%20on%20Strengthening%20Judicial%20Integrity%2C%20as%20revised%20at%20the%20Round%20Table%20Meeting%20of%20Chief%20Justices%20held%20at%20the%20Peace%20Palace%2C%20The%20Hague%2C%20November%2025-26%2C%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EBangalore%20Principles%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%2011-page%20detailed%20document%20which%20provides%20six%20%E2%80%9CValues%E2%80%9D%20divided%20into%2041%20%E2%80%9CApplication%20Principles%E2%80%9D%2C%20typical%20of%20UN%20guided%20agencies.%20The%20%E2%80%9Crestatement%E2%80%9D%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20a%20crisp%20three-page%20document%20which%20lists%2016%20%E2%80%9CValues%E2%80%9D%20of%20judicial%20life%20in%20fairly%20clear%20and%20direct%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EItem%209%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Crestatement%E2%80%9D%20reads%3A%20%E2%80%9CA%20Judge%20is%20expected%20to%20let%20his%20judgments%20speak%20for%20themselves.%20%3Cem%3EHe%20shall%20not%20give%20interview%20to%20the%20media%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(italics%20added).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESources%20of%20current%20concerns%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20sources%20of%20current%20concerns%20are%20a%20spate%20of%20interviews%20given%20by%20a%20former%20judge%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20soon%20after%20his%20retirement%20on%20December%2025%2C%202023%2C%20and%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dfnrl8Sdot5U%5C%22%3Einterview%20given%20by%20the%20current%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20PTI%20on%20January%2001%2C%202024.%20I%20will%20begin%20with%20the%20interviews%20given%20by%20former%20Justice%20Sanjay%20Kishan%20Kaul.%20Though%20he%20has%20given%20many%20interviews%2C%20I%20will%20limit%20my%20observations%20to%20the%20interview%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpdf.indianexpress.com%2Fpdfupload%2Fsubepaper%2Fie-delhi-26-12-2023.pdf%5C%22%3Epublished%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20December%2026%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20interview%20was%20published%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%20after%20his%20superannuation%2C%20it%20can%20be%20argued%20that%20he%20did%20not%20violate%20Item%209%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Crestatement%E2%80%9D.%20Technicalities%20such%20as%20whether%20the%20interview%20was%20actually%20conducted%20on%20the%20day%20of%20superannuation%20can%20be%20ignored%20but%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20letter%20and%20spirit%20of%20Item%209%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Crestatement%E2%80%9D%20remains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20substantive%20issues%2C%20Justice%20Kaul%20makes%20extensive%20comments%20on%20the%20judiciary%20dealing%20with%20the%20government%2C%20particularly%20%E2%80%98strong%E2%80%99%20governments.%20A%20few%20issues%20stand%20out.%20One%20pertains%20to%20what%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%9Ccheck%20and%20balance%E2%80%9D.%20A%20couple%20of%20statements%20are%20worth%20quoting%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20take%20from%201950.%20All%20of%20them%20will%20always%20be%20a%20little%20tough%20and%20that%20is%20part%20of%20the%20job.%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20anybody%20to%20interfere%20and%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20job%20is%20to%20check%20and%20balance%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20(italics%20added).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20weak%20opposition%20is%20also%20a%20problem.%20The%20absence%20of%20legislators%20from%20the%20opposition%20in%20the%20Parliament%20is%20an%20important%20factor.%20Maybe%20in%20public%20perception%2C%20it%20is%20their%20inability%20to%20politically%20handle%20the%20government.%20Now%2C%20the%20court%20cannot%20be%20placed%20to%20politically%20handle%20the%20government%E2%80%A6%20The%20court%20cannot%20be%20the%20opposition.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20judiciary%20is%20a%20check%20and%20balance%3C%2Fem%3E%20but%20to%20say%2C%20look%2C%20the%20government%20is%20doing%20this%20wrong%20and%20now%2C%20you%20have%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%E2%80%94%20is%20wrong%E2%80%9D%20(italics%20added).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20respect%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20state%20that%20the%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cjob%E2%80%9D%20is%20not%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccheck%20and%20balance%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20judiciary%20is%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccheck%20and%20balance%E2%80%9D.%20Its%20%3Cem%3Ejob%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20%3Cem%3Eto%20interpret%20the%20law%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20it%20is%3Cem%3E%20a%20part%20of%20the%20system%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20checks%20and%20balances.%20To%20clarify%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20a%20matter%20of%20semantics%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20pointing%20out%20that%20judges%2C%20and%20more%20particularly%20judges%20of%20the%20highest%20court%20of%20the%20land%2C%20whether%20serving%20or%20retired%2C%20are%20known%2C%20and%20expected%2C%20to%20use%20words%20with%20care.%20This%20creates%20a%20concern%20about%20how%20the%20%E2%80%98job%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20judiciary%20is%20seen%20and%20understood%20at%20the%20highest%20echelons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20issue%20is%20that%20of%20relations%20between%20the%20executive%20and%20the%20judiciary.%20For%20this%20again%2C%20a%20quotation%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%20we%20forget%20the%20past.%20When%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20executive%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20little%20pushback%20for%20the%20judiciary.%201990%20onwards%2C%20we%20have%20had%20coalition%20governments.%20So%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejudiciary%20was%20able%20to%20advance%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eits%20cause%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20sometimes%20even%20%3Cem%3Etransgress%20into%20some%20areas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20feel.%20But%20with%20a%20majority%20government%20coming%2C%20it%20was%20expected%20that%20some%20steps%20would%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20back%E2%80%9D%20(emphasis%20added).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20raises%20two%20concerns.%20One%2C%20what%20is%20judiciary%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98cause%E2%80%99%3F%20Two%2C%20why%20should%20judiciary%20%E2%80%98transgress%E2%80%99%20even%20if%20there%20is%20a%20coalition%20or%20a%20%E2%80%98weak%E2%80%99%20government%3F%20There%20can%20be%20more%20than%20one%20response%20to%20these%20two%20questions%20but%20it%20is%20doubtful%20many%20of%20the%20answers%20will%20do%20a%20favour%20to%20the%20institution%20that%20Justice%20Patanjali%20Sastry%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%3Cem%3ESentinel%20on%20the%20Qui%20Vive%3C%2Fem%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Kaul%E2%80%99s%20comments%20on%20what%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%9Cpolitico-legal%E2%80%9D%20cases%20which%20he%20terms%20as%20%E2%80%9Cbasically%20political%20decisions%E2%80%9D%20are%20valid%20but%20what%20he%20says%20about%20these%20getting%20%E2%80%9Chyped%20to%20different%20levels%20because%20of%20the%20political%20consequences%E2%80%9D%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20misunderstood%20as%20undue%20political%20sensitivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20again%20very%20correct%20in%20terming%20%E2%80%9Cbail%20hearings%20in%E2%80%A6political%20cases%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20complete%20waste%20of%20time%E2%80%9D%20but%20then%20again%2C%20he%20ends%20the%20paragraph%20with%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20government%20can%20weigh%20which%20cases%20it%20should%20litigate%E2%80%9D%2C%20leaving%20one%20thinking%20should%20he%20not%20have%20let%20the%20government%20know%20this%20in%20no%20uncertain%20terms%20when%20he%20was%20on%20the%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Crole%20of%20the%20Chief%20Justice%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20very%20registry-driven%20court%E2%80%9D%20and%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhatever%20happens%20is%20really%20between%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20and%20the%20registry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20takes%20one%20back%20to%20December%205%2C%202023%2C%20when%20it%20was%20discovered%20that%20two%20petitions%20seeking%20contempt%20of%20court%20action%20against%20the%20Union%20government%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20appointing%20judges%20whose%20names%20were%20cleared%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20collegium%2C%20listed%20before%20a%20bench%20headed%20by%20him%20seemed%20to%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20cause%20list%2C%20he%20was%20reported%20to%20have%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20clarify%20that%20it%20is%20not%20that%20I%20have%20deleted%20the%20matter%20or%20that%20I%20am%20unwilling%20to%20take%20the%20matter%2C%20both.%E2%80%9D%20When%20it%20was%20suggested%20that%20an%20explanation%20should%20be%20asked%20from%20the%20registry%2C%20he%20reportedly%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20sure%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20is%20aware%20of%20it%E2%80%A6Yesterday%20I%20found%20it%20was%20deleted.%20I%20checked%20up.%E2%80%9D%20When%20the%20counsel%20in%20the%20case%20said%20it%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20unusual%E2%80%9D%2C%20Justice%20Kaul%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsome-things-best-left-unsaid-sc-on-petitions-not-listed-for-hearing-9056132%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20reported%20to%20have%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Csome%20things%20are%20best%20left%20unsaid%20sometimes%E2%80%9D.%20The%20last%20statement%20about%20leaving%20some%20things%20%E2%80%98unsaid%E2%80%99%20says%20a%20lot!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20now%20come%20to%20the%20interview%20given%20by%20the%20CJI%20to%20PTI%20on%20January%201%2C%202024.%20The%20very%20first%20issue%20that%20comes%20to%20mind%20is%20item%209%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Crestatement%E2%80%9D%20which%20categorically%20says%20that%20a%20judge%20%E2%80%9Cshall%20not%20give%20interview%20to%20the%20media%E2%80%9D.%20It%20is%20correct%20that%20the%20first%20sentence%20refers%20to%20let%20%E2%80%9Cjudgments%20speak%20for%20themselves%E2%80%9D%20which%20the%20CJI%20alludes%20to%20later%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20but%20more%20on%20this%20later%20in%20this%20piece.%20One%20wonders%20whether%20the%20%E2%80%98Values%20of%20Judicial%20Life%E2%80%99%20still%20apply%20or%20have%20they%20been%20given%20a%20quiet%20burial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20substantive%20issues%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20in%20this%20case%20two%20issues%20stand%20out.%20One%20deals%20with%20the%20allocation%20of%20cases%20to%20different%20judges%20and%20the%20other%20with%20what%20has%20come%20to%20be%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20Ayodhya%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20some%20recent%20commentary%2C%20arising%20out%20of%20a%20few%20recent%20incidents%20including%2C%20but%20not%20limited%20to%2C%20Justice%20S.K.%20Kaul%E2%80%99s%20comment%20on%20December%205%2C%202023%20mentioned%20above%2C%20the%20CJI%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20very%20well-defined%20structures%20and%20processes%20for%20the%20allocation%20of%20cases.%E2%80%9D%20He%20then%20explained%20the%20system%20in%20some%20detail%20and%20went%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20bar%20as%20well%2C%20no%20lawyer%20can%20insist%20that%20I%E2%80%99ll%20have%20my%20case%20decided%20only%20by%20a%20particular%20judge%20because%20that%20does%20not%20do%20justice%20either%20to%20the%20credibility%20of%20individual%20judges%20or%20the%20purity%20of%20the%20administration%20of%20justice.%E2%80%9D%20He%20followed%20up%20this%20with%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20very%20very%20clear%20in%20my%20mind%20that%20if%20the%20credibility%20of%20the%20institution%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20to%20be%20maintained%2C%20we%20have%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20allocation%20of%20cases%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20is%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20lawyer-driven%20allocation.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20an%20allocation%20which%20we%20do%20in%20terms%20of%20our%20processes%20and%20systems%20which%20are%20laid%20down%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20Having%20said%20that%20I%20can%20only%20say%20that%2C%20well%2C%20you%20have%20to%20trust%20your%20decision%20makers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20repeated%20stress%20on%20%E2%80%9Clawyer-driven%20allocation%E2%80%9D%20is%20possibly%20an%20indicator%20of%20the%20over-sensitivity%20of%20the%20CJI%20to%20some%20recent%20incidents.%20In%20addition%20to%20Justice%20Kaul%E2%80%99s%20comment%20in%20open%20court%2C%20there%20was%20another%20incident%20in%20which%20a%20couple%20of%20senior%20lawyers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-registry-isnt-listing-cases-the-way-it-is-supposed-to-a-letter-to-the-cji%5C%22%3Ewrote%20%E2%80%98open%E2%80%99%20letters%20to%20the%20CJI%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20apparent%20inconsistencies%20in%20the%20process%20of%20case%20allocation.%20Based%20on%20the%20contents%20of%20these%20letters%2C%20which%20are%20available%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20there%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20any%20demand%20for%20a%20%E2%80%9Clawyer-driven%E2%80%9D%20allocation%3B%20all%20that%20the%20lawyers%20seemed%20to%20have%20been%20asking%20for%20was%20reasons%20for%20deviations%20from%20the%20%E2%80%9Csystems%20and%20processes%E2%80%9D%20specified%20in%20the%20documents%20of%20the%20court%20itself%2C%20namely%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20Rules%2C%202013%2C%20and%20Handbook%20on%20Practice%20and%20Procedure%20and%20Office%20Procedure%202017%2C%20published%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%20under%20Article%20145%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India.%20The%20concerns%20it%20raises%20are%20two-fold%3A%20(a)%20That%20there%20were%20apparent%20deviations%20from%20the%20laid%20down%20%E2%80%9Csystems%20and%20processes%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20(b)%20that%20the%20CJI%20chose%20to%20respond%20to%20these%20seeming%20deviations%20through%20a%20scripted%20interview%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20thereby%20violating%20Item%209%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CRestatement%20of%20Values%20of%20Judicial%20Life%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sci.gov.in%2Fpdf%2FJUD_2.pdf%5C%22%3EAyodhya%20judgment%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20indeed%20historic%2C%20though%20there%20have%20been%20all%20kinds%20of%20commentary%20on%20it.%20One%20of%20the%20issues%20that%20has%20been%20around%20ever%20since%20the%20judgment%20was%20pronounced%20on%20November%209%2C%202019%C2%A0has%20been%20that%20of%20the%20authorship%20of%20the%20judgement.%20This%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20the%20very%20first%20judgment%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20since%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20inception%20for%20which%20the%20name%20of%20the%20judge%20who%20actually%20wrote%20the%20unanimous%20judgment%20was%20not%20revealed.%20Since%20the%20CJI%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20five-judge%20bench%20who%20pronounced%20the%20judgment%2C%20when%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20authorship%2C%20he%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20five-judge%20bench%20sat%20to%20deliberate%20on%20the%20judgment%20as%20we%20all%20do%20before%20a%20judgment%20is%20pronounced%2C%20we%20all%20decided%20unanimously%20that%20this%20will%20be%20a%20judgment%20of%20the%20court%20and%20therefore%20there%20was%20no%20authorship%20ascribed%20to%20an%20individual%20judge.%20The%20case%20had%20a%20long%20history%2C%20of%20conflict%2C%20of%20diverse%20viewpoints%2C%20based%20on%20the%20history%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20all%20of%20us%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20bench%20decided%20that%20this%20will%20be%20a%20judgment%20of%20the%20court.%20The%20court%20will%20speak%20through%20one%20voice.%20The%20idea%20of%20doing%20so%20was%20to%20send%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20all%20of%20us%20stood%20together%20not%20only%20in%20the%20ultimate%20outcome%20but%20also%20in%20the%20reasons%20that%20were%20indicated%20in%20the%20judgment%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20we%20decided%20that%20it%20will%20read%20as%20a%20judgment%20of%20the%20court.%20Since%20we%20decided%20that%20it%20will%20read%20as%20a%20judgment%20of%20the%20court%2C%20it%20will%20always%20remain%20a%20judgment%20of%20the%20court.%20And%20I%20will%20close%20my%20answer%20with%20that.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20response%20creates%20uncertainty%20about%20all%20the%20unanimous%20judgments%20that%20the%20court%20has%20issued%20in%20its%20entire%20history.%20Simply%20stated%2C%20the%20uncertainty%20is%3A%20Are%20all%20other%20unanimous%20judgements%20not%20%E2%80%9Cjudgments%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%9D%3F%20The%20number%20of%20questions%20this%20response%20raises%20can%20be%20increased%20to%20match%20the%20number%20of%20times%20the%20phrase%20%E2%80%9Cjudgment%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%9D%20(five%20times)%20but%20that%20should%20not%20be%20necessary.%20The%20question%20stands%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConcluding%20comments%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArguably%2C%20the%20strongest%20pillar%20of%20the%20state%20which%20has%20been%20entrusted%20the%20onerous%20responsibility%20of%20safeguarding%20the%20most%20cherished%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20citizens%20under%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20by%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20the%20People%E2%80%9D%20seems%20to%20be%20on%20shaky%20ground%20itself.%20This%20does%20not%20portend%20well%20for%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20society%2C%20and%20the%20people.%20The%20hope%20of%20this%20article%20is%20that%20the%20judiciary%20will%20pull%20itself%20together%20in%20pursuit%20of%20its%20momentous%20task%20and%20it%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20all%20of%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20the%20People%E2%80%9D%2C%20to%20strengthen%20it%20so%20that%20it%20can%20become%20a%20true%20%3Cem%3ESentinel%20on%20the%20Qui%20Vive.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJagdeep%20S.%20Chhokar%20is%20a%20concerned%20citizen.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705576366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F18164057%2Fjustice-6983006_1280.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Frising-concerns-about-indias-judiciary%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20immediate%20cause%20of%20concern%20arises%20from%20the%20recent%20public%20utterances%20by%20two%20of%20the%20seniormost%20members%20of%20the%20highest%20judiciary%20in%20the%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Frising-concerns-about-indias-judiciary%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20process%20major%20lottery%20wins%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20seen%20everything%20from%20winning%20tickets%20in%20the%20laundry%20to%20people%20who%20almost%20claimed%20too%20late.%20Also%2C%20a%20giant%20snake.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20photo%20portrait%20of%20a%20smiling%20Andy%20Carter%2C%20a%20Winners'%20Advisor%20at%20UK%20lottery%20agency%20Camelot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F656deeb70ec98e92f74b9d71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndy%20Carter%2C%20a%20Winners'%20Advisor%20at%20UK%20lottery%20agency%20Camelot.%3Cp%3EDylan%20Nolte%20%2B%20Anthony%20Highet%2FCamelot%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndy%20Carter%20processes%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20major%20lottery%20wins%20%E2%80%94%20and%20has%20seen%20some%20close%20calls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20people%20almost%20missed%20out%20on%20a%20fortune%20by%20forgetting%20about%20their%20tickets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnother%20person%20accidentally%20put%20his%20winning%20ticket%20in%20the%20laundry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Andy%20Carter%2C%20who%20advises%20lottery%20winners%20for%20Camelot%2C%20the%20operator%20of%20the%20UK's%20National%20Lottery.%20His%20role%20is%20to%20process%20the%20prize%20money%20for%20major%20winners%20and%20ensure%20their%20ongoing%20welfare.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20is%20a%20real%20privilege%20because%20you%20get%20involved%20with%20someone%20at%20a%20stage%20of%20their%20life%20that%20they%20will%20never%2C%20ever%20forget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20there's%20a%20major%20winner%20in%20the%20UK's%20National%20Lottery%2C%20they%20get%20passed%20to%20my%20team.%20We're%20the%20people%20who%20handle%20winners%20of%20%C2%A350%2C000%20(%2463%2C000)%20and%20upwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20my%20job%20has%20a%20strict%20process%20from%20a%20regulatory%20point%20of%20view%2C%20we%20are%20also%20all%20about%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20try%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20lottery%20winners%20have%20great%20support%2C%20great%20access%20to%20advice%2C%20and%20that%20it%20should%20be%20a%20pleasant%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-lottery-winners-react-big-wins-unexpected-millionaires-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecause%20actually%20people%20are%20in%20shock%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20six-figure%20ticket%20in%20the%20laundry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20time%2C%20I%20dealt%20with%20a%20man%20who%20claimed%20his%20prize%20with%20us%20in%20plenty%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20an%20older%20man%20and%20he%20lived%20by%20himself%2C%20and%20he%20put%20his%20trousers%20in%20the%20washing%20machine%20along%20with%20his%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wallet%20was%20some%20cash%2C%20along%20with%20his%20winning%20ticket%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20worth%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20the%20wallet%20came%20out%20of%20the%20washing%20machine%20with%20everything%20intact.%20But%20the%20banknotes%20were%20all%20sort%20of%20screwed%20up.%20So%20he%20gave%20them%20a%20quick%20iron%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20also%20gave%20his%20ticket%20a%20quick%20iron.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20paper%20in%20our%20tickets%20reacts%20to%20heat%20%E2%80%94%20when%20the%20heat%20of%20an%20iron%20hits%20it%2C%20it%20goes%20black.%20Everything.%20All%20the%20numbers%20and%20all%20the%20barcodes%20%E2%80%94%20all%20the%20information%20we%20need%20on%20the%20front%20of%20the%20ticket%20just%20went%20black.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20horrified.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20he%20had%20already%20called%20in%20before%20this%20happened%2C%20we%20already%20had%20all%20the%20right%20information%20from%20him%2C%20the%20numbers%20and%20so%20forth.%20If%20he%20hadn't%20called%20in%2C%20we'd%20have%20had%20a%20real%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20investigation%2C%20and%20he%20had%20to%20wait%20a%20long%20time%20for%20that%20money%20to%20be%20paid%20%E2%80%94%20180%20days%20is%20the%20claim%20period%2C%20and%20we%20had%20to%20see%20whether%20or%20not%20anyone%20else%20would%20come%20forward%20with%20a%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20got%20paid%20eventually%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20a%20six-month%20wait%20because%20he%20ironed%20the%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20man%20who%20guarded%20his%20winning%20ticket%20with%20a%20snake%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20you've%20got%20this%20valuable%20piece%20of%20paper%2C%20and%20you%20are%20worried%20about%20it.%20Who%20do%20you%20trust%20to%20protect%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20to%20assure%20winners%20when%20they%20call%20that%20actually%2C%20look%2C%20yes%2C%20we%20need%20this%20ticket%2C%20but%20you've%20given%20us%20the%20details%20now.%20If%20someone%20were%20to%20steal%20that%20ticket%2C%20you%20could%20ring%20us%20and%20we%20have%20procedures%20to%20put%20a%20stop%20on%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20still%2C%20occasionally%20they%20come%20up%20with%20some%20odd%20places%20to%20hide%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20seen%20people%20keep%20their%20tickets%20in%20the%20dictionary%2C%20under%20%26quot%3BW%26quot%3B%20for%20%26quot%3Bwinner.%26quot%3B%20They%20keep%20it%20tucked%20behind%20photo%20frames%20of%20loved%20ones.%20Some%20women%20keep%20it%20in%20their%20bras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20this%20one%20guy%20who%20said%20that%20someone%20%E2%80%94%20I%20forget%20the%20name%2C%20%26quot%3BSid%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BBert%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20whatever%20%E2%80%94%20was%20%26quot%3Bguarding%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20this%20was%20a%20friend.%20But%20then%20he%20pointed%20over%2C%20and%20there's%20this%20snake%20in%20a%20tank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20there%20was%20this%20big%20pile%20of%20rocks%2C%20and%20then%20underneath%20the%20rocks%20was%20a%20rubber%20envelope.%20Apparently%20the%20snake%20doesn't%20like%20rubber%20and%20won't%20touch%20it.%20And%20in%20there%20was%20the%20ticket%2C%20because%20no%20one%20was%20going%20to%20try%20to%20put%20their%20hands%20in%20past%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20like%20snakes%3F%26quot%3B%20and%20gets%20it%20out%20and%20puts%20it%20around%20my%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20kids%20were%20young%20at%20the%20time%20and%20I%20thought%2C%20oh%2C%20this%20will%20impress%20them%2C%20their%20dad%20holding%20a%20snake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%2490%20million%20tucked%20behind%20the%20sun%20visor%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20massive%20Euromillions%20winner%20from%20Boston%2C%20in%20Lincolnshire%2C%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20came%20forward%20to%20claim%2C%20for%20weeks%20and%20weeks.%20And%20we%20were%20publicizing%20it%2C%20saying%20in%20the%20media%3A%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20the%20Euromillions%20winner%20in%20Boston%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyway%2C%20this%20guy%20came%20forward%20about%20two%2C%20three%20days%20before%20Christmas.%20He%20was%20a%20builder%20or%20something%20like%20that%2C%20and%20the%20ticket%20had%20been%20in%20the%20sun%20visor%20of%20his%20van%20all%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe'll%20have%20forgotten%20about%20it.%20He%20would've%20got%20in%20his%20van%2C%20stopped%20off%20at%20a%20gas%20station%20to%20get%20a%20sandwich%2C%20bought%20a%20ticket%2C%20got%20back%20into%20his%20van%2C%20and%20put%20it%20behind%20the%20sun%20visor%20along%20with%20bits%20of%20paper%2C%20receipts%2C%20and%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20worth%20%C2%A370%20million%20(%2489%20million).%20Huge.%20Huge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ENote%20to%20lottery%20players%3A%20tidy%20your%20room%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20player%20who%20was%2018%20or%2019%2C%20something%20like%20that%2C%20who%20lived%20at%20home%20with%20his%20mom%20and%20dad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe'd%20been%20tidying%20his%20room%20and%20had%20found%20the%20ticket%2C%20worth%20a%20couple%20of%20hundred%20thousand%20pounds.%20He%20hadn't%20even%20known%20he%20had%20it%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20just%20a%20case%20of%20his%20mom%20telling%20him%20to%20tidy%20his%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20180%20days%20to%20pay%20a%20prize%20out%20after%20a%20draw%2C%20and%20I%20think%20he