o%20oversee%20and%20regulate%20coaching%20centres.%20According%20to%20these%20guidelines%2C%20coaching%20centres%20are%20prohibited%20from%20admitting%20students%20below%20the%20age%20of%2016%2C%20and%20enrollment%20is%20permitted%20only%20after%20successful%20completion%20of%20the%20secondary%20school%20examination.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EConditions%20for%20registration%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20coaching%20centre%20shall%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEngage%20tutors%20with%20qualifications%20lower%20than%20graduation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMake%20misleading%20promises%20or%20guarantees%20of%20ranks%20or%20good%20marks%20to%20parents%2Fstudents%20for%20enrolling%20them%20in%20the%20coaching%20centre.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEnroll%20students%20below%2016%20years%20of%20age%3B%20student%20enrollment%20should%20only%20occur%20after%20the%20secondary%20school%20examination.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPublish%20or%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20publication%20of%20any%20misleading%20advertisement%20related%20to%20claims%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly%2C%20regarding%20the%20quality%20of%20coaching%2C%20facilities%20offered%2C%20or%20the%20results%20obtained%20by%20the%20coaching%20centre%C2%A0or%20its%20students.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBe%20registered%20if%20it%20has%20less%20than%20the%20minimum%20space%20requirement%20per%20student.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20objectives%20of%20these%20guidelines%20include%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEstablishing%20a%20framework%20for%20the%20registration%20and%20regulation%20of%20coaching%20centres.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDefining%20minimum%20standard%20requirements%20for%20the%20operation%20of%20coaching%20centres.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESafeguarding%20the%20interests%20of%20students%20enrolled%20in%20coaching%20centres.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EEncouraging%20coaching%20centres%C2%A0to%20prioritise%20co-curricular%20activities%20for%20comprehensive%20student%20development.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EProviding%20career%20guidance%20and%20psychological%20counseling%20to%20ensure%20the%20mental%20well-being%20of%20students.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20registration%20process%20for%20coaching%20centres%20involves%20submitting%20applications%2C%20undergoing%20renewal%20procedures%2C%20and%20complying%20with%20specified%20conditions.%20Registration%20conditions%20include%20hiring%20qualified%20tutors%2C%20avoiding%20deceptive%20promises%2C%20admitting%20students%20above%20the%20age%20of%2016%2C%20and%20implementing%20a%20counseling%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.education.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fupload_files%2Fmhrd%2Ffiles%2FGuideliens_Coaching_Centres_en.pdf%5C%22%3EThe%20guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20address%20fee-related%20matters%2C%20emphasising%20fair%20and%20reasonable%20charges%2C%20transparent%20fee%20receipts%2C%20and%20detailed%20prospectuses.%20Refund%20policies%20are%20outlined%2C%20and%20fee%20adjustments%20are%20specified%20for%20students%20leaving%20a%20course%20prematurely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfrastructure%20requirements%20mandate%20a%20minimum%20space%20allocation%20per%20student%2C%20adherence%20to%20safety%20codes%2C%20provision%20of%20first%20aid%20and%20medical%20facilities%2C%20electrification%2C%20ventilation%2C%20lighting%2C%20clean%20drinking%20water%2C%20and%20security%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20class-related%20aspects%2C%20the%20guidelines%20stress%20timely%20completion%20of%20classes%2C%20avoiding%20conflicts%20with%20regular%20school%20hours%2C%20offering%20support%20classes%2C%20ensuring%20breaks%20to%20reduce%20pressure%2C%20weekly%20offs%2C%20and%20limiting%20daily%20coaching%20hours.%20Co-curricular%20activities%20are%20encouraged%2C%20and%20counseling%20sessions%20on%20life%20skills%20and%20various%20topics%20are%20recommended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20guidelines%20aim%20to%20establish%20a%20regulatory%20framework%20that%20ensures%20the%20well-being%20and%20proper%20education%20of%20students%20attending%20coaching%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECancellation%20of%20registration%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20certificate%20of%20registration%20granted%20to%20a%20coaching%20centre%20may%20be%20canceled%20at%20any%20time%20if%20the%20competent%20authority%20is%20satisfied%20that%20the%20centre%20has%20violated%20any%20of%20the%20guidelines'%20provisions%20or%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20registration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20competent%20authority%20must%20provide%20the%20certificate%20holder%20with%20a%20reasonable%20opportunity%20to%20present%20their%20case%20before%20making%20such%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20initiated%20measures%20in%20alignment%20with%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%2C%20addressing%20the%20Common%20University%20Entrance%20Test%20(CUET)%2C%20conducting%20entrance%20examinations%20in%2013%20regional%20languages%2C%20expanding%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20Higher%20Education%20Institutions%20(HEIs)%2C%20and%20establishing%20high-quality%20Higher%20Education%20Institutions.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTo%20assist%20students%20in%20preparing%20for%20NEET%20(UG)%20and%20JEE%20(Main)%20entrance%20examinations%2C%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%20has%20launched%20the%20'National%20Test%20Abhyas'%20Mobile%20App%2C%20providing%20candidates%20with%20access%20to%20high-quality%20mock%20tests%20online%20free%20of%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705576140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-12%2Feducation-generic_650x400_71512568884.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fcoaching-centres-cannot-enroll-students-below-16-years-government-4885466%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20guidelines%20aim%20to%20establish%20a%20regulatory%20framework%20that%