ikes%20on%20insurgent%20groups%20in%20Iran.%20It%20comes%20two%20days%20after%20Tehran%20attacked%20what%20it%20called%20%E2%80%9Cterrorist%20targets%E2%80%9D%20inside%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%E2%80%99s%20official%20IRNA%20news%20agency%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.irna.ir%2Fnews%2F85358107%2FIran-summons-Pakistan-charg%25C3%25A9-d-affaires-to-protest-missile-attack%5C%22%3Enine%20people%20were%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20this%20attack.%20The%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%20news%20channel%20cited%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20interior%20minister%20as%20telling%20state%20media%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2024%2F1%2F18%2Fpakistan-iran-attacks-live-at-least-7-killed-near-irans-southeast-border%5C%22%3Eall%20nine%20were%20foreign%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20morning%20Pakistan%20undertook%20a%20series%20of%20highly%20coordinated%20and%20specifically%20targeted%20precision%20military%20strikes%20against%20terrorist%20hideouts%20in%20Sistan-o-Baluchistan%20province%20of%20Iran%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20statement%20by%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cnumber%20of%20terrorists%20were%20killed%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20added%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20last%20several%20years%2C%20in%20our%20engagements%20with%20Iran%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20consistently%20shared%20its%20serious%20concerns%20about%20the%20safe%20havens%20and%20sanctuaries%20enjoyed%20by%20Pakistani%20origin%20terrorists%20calling%20themselves%20Sarmachars%20on%20the%20ungoverned%20spaces%20inside%20Iran.%20Pakistan%20also%20shared%20multiple%20dossiers%20with%20concrete%20evidence%20of%20the%20presence%20and%20activities%20of%20these%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20action%20on%20our%20serious%20concerns%2C%20these%20so-called%20Sarmachars%20continued%20to%20spill%20the%20blood%20of%20innocent%20Pakistanis%20with%20impunity.%20This%20morning%E2%80%99s%20action%20was%20taken%20in%20light%20of%20credible%20intelligence%20of%20impending%20large%20scale%20terrorist%20activities%20by%20these%20so%20called%20Sarmachars.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20has%20Iran%20said%20about%20the%20strikes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIRNA%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.irna.ir%2Fnews%2F85358107%2FIran-summons-Pakistan-charg%25C3%25A9-d-affaires-to-protest-missile-attack%5C%22%3EIran%20had%20summoned%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20charge%20d%E2%80%99affaires%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20protest%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20attack%2C%20and%20Tasnim%2C%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20semi-official%20news%20agency%2C%20said%20Iran%20had%20sought%20an%20explanation%20from%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIRNA%20also%20reported%20explosions%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20restive%20southeastern%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSeveral%20explosions%20have%20been%20heard%20in%20several%20areas%20around%20the%20city%20of%20Saravan%2C%E2%80%9D%20IRNA%20said%2C%20quoting%20an%20official%20in%20the%20Sistan-Baluchistan%20province%20where%20the%20city%20is%20situated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%E2%80%99s%20semi-official%20Young%20Journalist%20Club%20news%20agency%20had%20earlier%20reported%20that%20at%20least%20three%20women%20and%20four%20children%20were%20among%20those%20killed%20in%20one%20of%20the%20explosions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20country%E2%80%99s%20Mehr%20news%20agency%20said%20that%20several%20people%20were%20wounded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20in%20the%20Iranian%20strikes%20on%20targets%20in%20Pakistan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Iran%20said%20that%20it%20struck%20bases%20belonging%20to%20Jaish%20al-Adl%2C%20a%20Sunni%20militant%20group%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20that%20two%20children%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20incident%20and%20condemned%20the%20strikes%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunprovoked%20violation%E2%80%9D%20of%20its%20airspace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20Pakistan%20recalled%20its%20ambassador%20from%20Iran%20and%20blocked%20Tehran%E2%80%99s%20envoy%20from%20returning%20to%20Islamabad%20following%20the%20strikes%20from%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20reactions%20to%20the%20attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20said%20it%20is%20willing%20to%20help%20%E2%80%98de-escalate%E2%80%99%20the%20situation%20between%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Chinese%20side%20sincerely%20hopes%20that%20the%20two%20sides%20can%20exercise%20calm%20and%20restraint%20and%20avoid%20an%20escalation%20of%20tension%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20AFP%20news%20agency%20quoted%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Mao%20Ning%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20willing%20to%20play%20a%20constructive%20role%20in%20de-escalating%20the%20situation%20if%20both%20sides%20so%20wish.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfghanistan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20the%20violence%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20was%20%E2%80%9Calarming%E2%80%9D%20and%20called%20on%20them%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexercise%20restraint%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20responded%20to%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20missile%20strike%20on%20Pakistan%20by%20saying%20it%20%E2%80%98understood%E2%80%99%20actions%20that%20countries%20took%20in%20%E2%80%98self-defence%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20matter%20between%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan.%20Insofar%20as%20India%20is%20concerned%2C%20we%20have%20an%20uncompromising%20position%20of%20zero%20tolerance%20towards%20terrorism.%20We%20understand%20actions%20that%20countries%20take%20in%20their%20self-defence%2C%E2%80%9D%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%2C%20who%20is%20spokesperson%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20external%20affairs%20ministry%2C%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20backing%20of%20the%