0in%20Austin.%20It%20also%20gives%20us%20a%20chance%20to%20play%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20market%3A%20we%20sold%20our%20old%20residence%20before%20a%20potential%20downturn%20and%20we%20may%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20buy%20back%20in%20later%20on%20if%20prices%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222444%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20daughters%20in%20their%20playroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a80ebe43bb77284b9dca7a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222144%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAs%20our%20family%20grew%20older%2C%20we%20found%20we%20needed%20less%20space%20for%20things%20like%20playrooms.%3Cp%3ECork%20Gaines%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20first%20real-estate%20agent%20we%20interviewed%20in%20August%20warned%20us%20about%20a%20possible%20impending%20downturn%20in%20the%20local%20housing%20market%20and%20suggested%20we%20list%20the%20house%20for%20about%2015%25%20below%20what%20similar%20houses%20had%20sold%20for%20in%20previous%20months.%20We%20stood%20firm%20on%20our%20original%20price%20of%20%24750%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20knew%20a%20drop%20in%20housing%20prices%20in%20the%20Austin%20area%20was%20possible%20and%20even%20likely.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Faustin-housing-market-about-hit-turning-point-1853870%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERealtor.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20projected%20a%2012%25%20drop%20in%20housing%20prices%20for%20the%20area%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20be%20sure%2C%20prices%20were%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Faustin-housing-market-about-hit-turning-point-1853870%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E55%25%20above%20prepandemic%20levels%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20were%20confident%20it%20was%20too%20early%20to%20panic%20even%20though%20it%20was%20taking%20houses%20longer%20to%20sell%20and%2C%20recently%2C%20there's%20been%20an%20increase%20in%20