%20the%20new%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20compound%20five-year%20growth%20rate%20for%20the%20No.%201%20job%20on%20the%20list%2C%20chief%20growth%20officer%2C%20was%2041%25%2C%20based%20on%20rates%20shared%20with%20BI.%20Government%20program%20analyst%20and%20environment%20health%20safety%20manager%2C%20which%20ranked%20No.%202%20and%20No.%203%20respectively%2C%20both%20had%20rates%20around%2039%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%20I%20think%20the%20list%20has%20a%20nice%20diversity%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20there's%20something%20on%20it%20kind%20of%20for%20everyone%20regardless%20of%20your%20educational%20background%2C%20your%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Seaman%2C%20senior%20managing%20editor%20for%20jobs%20%26amp%3B%20career%20development%20at%20LinkedIn%20News%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20list%20is%20based%20on%20several%20years%20of%20data%2C%20Seaman%20said%20that%20opportunities%20in%20these%20roles%20are%20unlikely%20to%20quickly%20dry%20up.%20Instead%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20like%20to%20call%20it%20sustainable%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20Seaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20areas%20where%20companies%20have%20shown%20consistent%20interest%20and%20commitment%2C%26quot%3B%20Seaman%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20who%20are%20seeing%20this%20list%2C%20people%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20plan%20their%20careers%2C%20they%20could%20look%20at%20this%20list%20without%20having%20to%20worry%20that%20these%20jobs%20are%20going%20to%20fall%20off%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Earth%20in%20a%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20looking%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-land-dream-job-interviews-tech-founders-advice-career-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eland%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20one%20of%20these%20jobs%20should%20think%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-want-soft-skills-good-communication-teamwork-leadership-energetic-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eskills%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20need.%20Seaman%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20skills%20needed%20to%20do%20any%20job%20is%20evolving%20rapidly%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20more%20and%20more%20employers%20are%20doing%20skills-first%20hiring%2C%20so%20they%20may%20place%20less%20emphasis%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20their%20past%20job%20titles%2C%20per%20Seaman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20would%20suggest%20to%20people%20is%20think%20about%20the%20skills%20they%20have%20and%20the%20skills%20that%20are%20required%20to%20do%20these%20jobs%2C%26quot%3B%20Seaman%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20new%20report%20notes%20some%20of%20these%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20see%20that%20you%20want%20to%20go%20into%20sustainability%20and%20maybe%20you're%20missing%20some%20big%20skills%20on%20that%20list%2C%20then%20you%20want%20to%20work%20toward%20filling%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20Seaman%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20even%20if%20you're%20coming%20from%20a%20different%20industry%20or%20a%20different%20background%2C%20it%20helps%20you%20pivot%20into%20that%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20the%2015%20fastest-growing%20jobs%20in%20the%20US%20jobs%20per%20the%20new%20LinkedIn%20report.%20Most%20common%20skills%20noted%20below%20%26quot%3Bwere%20derived%20from%20the%20top%20skills%20most%20unique%20to%20each%20title%20among%20members%20who%20have%20ever%20held%20that%20title%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%26quot%3B%20per%20the%20report.%20The%20median%20years%20of%20prior%20experience%20noted%20for%20jobs%20below%20%26quot%3Bwas%20calculated%20using%20the%20median%20years%20of%20work%20experience%20held%20prior%20to%20starting%20in%20the%20featured%20title%20for%20members%20hired%20within%20the%20methodology%20timeframe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E15.%20Director%20of%20land%20acquisition%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Four%20people%20sta