insider.com%2Fweight-loss-glp-1-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-mounjaro-effects-future-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMounjaro%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20drug%20manufactured%20for%20diabetes%20but%20at%20the%20time%20used%20off-label%20for%20weight%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EInjuring%20her%20back%20was%20an%20'aha'%20moment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrunch%20was%20always%20active%2C%20playing%20sports%20and%20going%20to%20the%20gym%2C%20but%20as%20a%20busy%20neurosurgeon%20and%20mother%20to%20two%20children%2C%20she%20relied%20on%20convenience%20foods%20and%20her%20weight%20crept%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20had%20various%20aches%20and%20pains%2C%20which%20she%20believed%20were%20exacerbated%20by%20her%20weight.%20Things%20came%20to%20a%20head%20in%202018%20when%20she%20bent%20over%20to%20pick%20up%20her%20baby%20boy%20and%20tore%20a%20disc%20in%20her%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Baha%26quot%3B%20moment%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20way%20I%20could%20see%20a%20change%20happening%20was%20completely%20changing%20my%20way%20of%20thinking%20and%20my%20way%20of%20approaching%20my%20health%20and%20my%20lifestyle%2C%26quot%3B%20Grunch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20her%20reading%2C%20she%20learned%20that%20she%20needed%20to%20take%20a%20holistic%20approach%20to%20weight%20loss%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20think%20long-term%20for%20results%20to%20last%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EGrunch%20did%20intermittent%20fasting%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGrunch%20decided%20to%20try%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fconditions-symptoms%2Ffasting-for-weight-loss%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eintermittent%20fasting%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20eating%20all%20her%20food%20for%20the%20day%20in%20a%20six-hour%20window.%20She%20initially%20tried%20shorter%20eating%20windows%2C%20which%20she%20found%20unsustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearch%20shows%20that%20there%20is%20nothing%20special%20about%20intermittent%20fasting%20for%20weight%20loss%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fintermittent-fasting-52-diet-reasons-why-people-quit-fasting-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eit%20doesn't%20work%20for%20everyone%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20can%20be%20challenging%20to%20maintain.%20But%20it%20helps%20some%20people%20stick%20to%20a%20calorie%20deficit%2C%20which%20is%20required%20for%20weight%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrunch%20also%20swapped%20from%20a%20fast-food%20heavy%20diet%20to%20one%20high%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-protein-daily-diet-to-lose-body-fat-keep-muscle-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eprotein%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20whole%20foods%2C%20and%20lower-carb.%20Protein%20is%20helpful%20for%20weight%20loss%20because%20it%20keeps%20you%20feeling%20full%20and%20helps%20the%20body%20maintain%20muscle%20during%20a%20calorie%20deficit.%20Carbs%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20aren't%20inherently%20fattening%2C%20but%20Grunch%20just%20felt%20better%20eating%20less%20of%20them%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr.%20Betsy%20Grunch%20before%20and%20after%20losing%20weight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a6bb6843bb77284b9d5fd9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Betsy%20Grunch%20before%20and%20after%20losing%20weight%3Cp%3EDr.%20Betsy%20Grunch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-lose-weight-without-counting-calories-fat-loss-tips-2020-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecounted%20calories%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20and%20off%20to%20ensure%20she%20was%20in%20a%20deficit%2C%20but%20found%20it%20too%20time-consuming%20to%20do%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20I%20started%20implementing%20those%20changes%2C%20the%20weight%20