ed%20to%20look%20and%20feel%20as%20fit%20as%20possible%2C%20so%20she%20decided%20to%20talk%20to%20her%20doctor%20about%20taking%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbody-image-distortion-after-weight-loss-common-glp-1-drugs-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGLP-1%20medication%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20buzzy%20class%20of%20appetite-suppressing%20drugs%20that%20includes%20Ozempic%20and%20Wegovy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20drugs%20can%20carry%20unpleasant%20side%20effects%20including%20nausea%20and%20constipation%2C%20and%20after%20discussing%20the%20pros%20and%20cons%20of%20the%20various%20types%2C%20Grunch%20started%20taking%20the%20diabetes%20drug%20Mounjaro%2C%20a%20brand%20name%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lilly-mounjaro-zepbound-approved-weight-loss-stronger-than-wegovy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etirzepatide%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20now%20marketed%20for%20weight%20loss%20as%20Zepbound.%20Research%20suggests%20it's%20even%20more%20effective%20than%20semaglutide%2C%20marketed%20as%20Wegovy%20for%20weight%20loss%20and%20Ozempic%20for%20diabetes%2C%20enabling%20non-diabetic%20people%20to%20lose%20between%2015%20to%2020%25%20of%20their%20body%20weight%20on%20average.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20March%20and%20September%202023%2C%20Grunch%20lost%2030%20pounds%20on%20the%20drug%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20kind%20of%20weird%2C%26quot%3B%20Grunch%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpros-cons-ozempic-semaglutide-before-after-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Efood%20was%20not%20a%20part%20of%20my%20brain%20anymore%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20it%20completely%20separated%20the%20way%20I%20felt%20about%20food%20and%20the%20connection%20I%20had%20with%20certain%20foods.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrunch%20was%20%26quot%3Bobsessed%26quot%3B%20with%20peanut%20butter%2C%20for%20insta