-husband-on-scooty-4885986%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpalwal-hodal-haryana-woman-tricks-cops-whisks-away-jailed-husband-on-scooty-4885986%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Reddit%20User%20Praised%20For%20Not%20Swapping%20Airplane%20Seats%20With%20Pregnant%20Woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Reddit%20user%20is%20being%20praised%20online%20for%20refusing%20to%20swap%20seats%20with%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20on%20an%20airplane.%20Posting%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BAITAH%26quot%3B%20subreddit%20on%20Saturday%2C%20user%20'hahahajump'%2C%20asked%20the%20Reddit%20community%20to%20weigh%20in%20on%20his%20story%2C%20titled%2C%20%26quot%3BAITAH%20(Am%20I%20the%20a**hole%20here)%20for%20not%20giving%20up%20my%20free%20upgraded%20exit%20gate%20seat%20to%20a%20couple%20...%20wanting%20%5Bto%20be%5D%20sitting%20together%26quot%3B.%20In%20the%20post%2C%20the%20user%20described%20a%20recent%2014-hour%20flight%20from%20Asia%2C%20with%20an%20economy%20ticket%20booked%20%26quot%3Bas%20normal%26quot%3B.%20The%20person%20revealed%20that%20they%20refused%20to%20accommodate%20a%20man's%20request%20to%20switch%20seats%20with%20his%20pregnant%20wife%20who%20was%20seated%20many%20rows%20behind%20on%20the%20airplane.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20post%2C%20the%20Reddit%20user%20was%20offered%20a%20chance%20to%20move%20to%20an%20aisle%20seat%20in%20the%20emergency%20exit%20row%20-%20something%20that%20they%20%26quot%3Bhappily%20accepted%20instantly%26quot%3B.%20But%20the%20minute%20the%20person%20moved%20to%20the%20new%20seat%2C%20a%20young%20man%20in%20his%2020s%20already%20sitting%20in%20the%20row%20asked%20if%20his%20pregnant%20wife%20could%20have%20the%20exit-row%20seat%20as%20she%20was%20not%20comfortable%20in%20her%20existing%20seat%20many%20rows%20behind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-embed-height%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FAITAH%2Fcomments%2F195ga7j%2Faitah_for_not_giving_up_my_free_upgraded_exit%2F%5C%22%3EAITAH%20for%20not%20giving%20up%20my%20free%20upgraded%20exit%20gate%20seat%20to%20couple%20(pregnant%20wife%20sitting%20far%20behind)%20wanting%20be%20sitting%20together(%20husband%20bought%20exit%20gate%20seat%20next%20to%20me%20already)%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cnby%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fuser%2Fhahahajump%2F%5C%22%3Eu%2Fhahahajump%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FAITAH%2F%5C%22%3EAITAH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHahahajump%20wondered%20why%20the%20man%20had%20only%20paid%20for%20a%20premium%20seat%20for%20himself%20and%20not%20for%20his%20own%20wife.%20%26quot%3BMy%20brain%20just%20instantly%20responded%2C%20'Oh%2C%20but%20you%20have%20a%20bigger%20seat.%20Why%20don't%20you%20switch%20with%20hers%3F'%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20user.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHahahajump%20refused%20to%20switch%20seats%20and%20the%20man's%20face%20%26quot%3Binstantly%26quot%3B%20sank%2C%20the%20post%20read.%20As%20the%20flight%20took%20off%2C%20the%20user%20said%20that%20they%20were%20very%20tired%20and%20%26quot%3Bended%20up%20instantly%20falling%20asleep%20with%20my%20headphones%20on%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20poster%20(OP)%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20woke%20up%203%20or%204%20hours%20later%26quot%3B%20only%20to%20find%20a%20new%20seatmate%20-%20the%20man's%20pregnant%20wife.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20story%20after%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Redditor%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20had%20zero%20communication%2C%20which%20was%20perfect%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OP%20does%20not%20believe%20that%20they%20did%20anything%20out%20of%20line%20in%20terms%20of%20behaviour%20regarding%20the%20seat-switching%20request.%20However%2C%20their%20friends%20and%20family%20said%20that%20the%20traveller%20should%20have%20given%20up%20the%20seat%20for%20the%20person's%20wife%20so%20that%20the%20couple%20could%20sit%20together.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I%20really%20feel%2C%20Why%20%5Bdidn't%5D%20the%20husband%20switch%20his%20%5Bseat%5D%20as%20he%20was%20already%20in%20the%20better%20seat%3F%26quot%3B%20wrote%20hahahajump.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20me%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teachers-aide-admits-to-having-sex-with-numerous-teenage-boys-4885546%5C%22%3EUS%20Teacher's%20Aide%20Admits%20To%20Having%20Sex%20With%20%26quot%3BNumerous%26quot%3B%20Teenage%20Boys%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Reddit%20post%20has%20accumulated%20more%20than%204%2C000%20upvotes.%20In%20the%20comments%20section%2C%20while%20some%20assured%20the%20user%20that%20they%20were%20not%20%26quot%3BNTA%20(Not%20the%20A**hole)%26quot%3B%20for%20keeping%20the%20seat%20upgrade%2C%20others%20were%20critical%20of%20how%20the%20man%20seemingly%20planned%20on%20exploiting%20the%20system%20for%20a%20better%20seat%20for%20his%20wife.%20Some%20users%20were%20also%20surprised%20a%20pregnant%20woman%20was%20permitted%20to%20sit%20in%20the%20exit%20row%20as%20people%20who%20are%20in%20the%20exit%20row%20must%20agree%20to%20assist%20during%20an%20emergency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNta%20that%20was%20a%20great%20question%20for%20the%20man.%20Why%20would%20he%20expect%20a%20stranger%20to%20give%20up%20their%20seat%20when%20he%20wasn't%20willing%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20playing%20on%20you%20being%20sympathetic.%20NTAH.%20It's%20the%20husband's%20responsibility%20to%20make%20sure%20his%20wife%20is%20comfortable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExit%20seats%20normally%20come%20with%20a%20responsibility%20to%20be%20able%20to%20help%20open%20doors%20in%20an%20emergency.%20Older%2C%20younger%20or%20disabled%20can't%20sit%20there.%20I'm%20guessing%20a%20pregnant%20person%20would%20also%20be%20considered%20not%20phys