irst%20taste%20is%20so%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quality%20of%20plant-based%20meat%20varies%20massively%20between%20brands%2C%20which%20is%20why%20so%20many%20restaurants%20and%20fast-food%20outlets%20emphasize%20which%20brands%20their%20plant-based%20dishes%20are%20made%20with%2C%20Firth%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20go%20to%20a%20pub%20and%20they%20don't%20tell%20you%20what%20their%20vegan%20patty%20is%2C%20it's%20a%20gamble%20and%20it%20could%20be%20wonderful%2C%20but%20it%20also%20could%20just%20be%20made%20in-house%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlant-based%20milk%20and%20meat%20have%20become%20much%20more%20readily%20available%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20but%20vegan%20cheese%20is%20where%20more%20development%20is%20needed%2C%20Theasby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20last%20bastion%20of%20plant-based%20food%20really%20is%20cheese%2C%26quot%3B%20Theasby%20said.%20%26quot%3BCheese%20is%20something%20that%20people%20really%20love%2C%20they%20get%20really%20passionate%20about.%20Vegan%20cheese%20at%20the%20moment%20is%20good%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20better.%20I%20think%20that%20is%20definitely%20a%20product%20category%20that%20will%20get%20better%20in%20the%20very%20near%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20have%20released%20six%20cookbooks%20as%20well%20as%20a%20guide%20to%20vegan%20living%20and%20sell%20a%20range%20of%20products%20at%20UK%20grocery%20stores.%20Bosh!%20has%20also%20just%20launched%20a%20partnership%20with%20Costa%20Coffee%2C%20the%20UK's%20largest%20coffee-shop%20chain%20with%20more%20than%202%2C600%20stores%2C%20to%20sell%20eight%20plant-based%20items%2C%20including%20a%20fajita%20wrap%20and%20rocky%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223992%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Henry%20Firth%20and%20Ian%20Theasby%2C%20of%20vegan%20brand%20Bosh!%2C%20pose%20with%20a%20selection%20of%20vegan%20food%20and%20drinks%20from%20Costa%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20