0is%20that%20time%20of%20the%20year%20when%20predictions%20are%20made%20for%20marketing%20in%20the%20new%20year%20in%20order%20to%20prioritise%20action%20plans.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGoing%20with%20the%20spirit%20of%20what%20Niels%20had%20said%2C%20I%20will%20only%20pick%20up%20those%20trends%20that%20have%20been%20underway%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20and%20will%20continue%20this%20year.%20Keep%20a%20sharp%20eye%20on%20these%20trends%20to%20strategise%20your%20year%20for%20competitive%20edge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20friend%20and%20business%20adviser%20Stan%20Davis%20first%20mooted%20the%20idea%20of%20mass%20customisation.%20Advertising%20executive%20Don%20Peppers%20extended%20the%20idea%20to%20one-to-one%20marketing.%20Personalised%20marketing%20has%20been%20gaining%20traction%20and%2C%20in%202024%2C%20I%20expect%20it%20to%20become%20more%20sophisticated%20with%20AI%20and%20analytics.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECMOs%20will%20leverage%20Generative%20AI%2C%20machine%20learning%20and%20data%20analytics%20to%20deliver%20hyper-personalised%20content%20and%20experiences%20across%20various%20touch%20points%2C%20catering%20to%20individual%20preferences%20and%20behaviour.%20Hyper-personalisation%20will%20remain%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20marketing%20strategies%20this%20year.%20Companies%20like%20Amazon%20have%20been%20using%20advanced%20data%20analytics%20to%20personalise%20customer%20experiences.%20Use%20algorithm%20to%20analyse%20browsing%20and%20purchase%20history%20to%20offer%20recommendations%2C%20and%20significantly%20influence%20purchase%20decisions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENext%20trend%20is%20the%20pervasive%20use%20of%20marketing%20technology%20or%20MarTech%20by%20marketers%20across%20the%20spectrum.%20AI%20will%20play%20an%20increasingly%20prominent%20role%20in%20MarTech.%20CMOs%20will%20harness%20AI%20for%20predictive%20analytics%2C%20chatbots%2C%20content%20generation%2C%20customer%20segmentation%2C%20and%20enhancing%20overall%20customer%20experiences.%20They%20will%20increasingly%20rely%20on%20AI-driven%20tools%20to%20automate%20repetitive%20tasks%2C%20optimise%20ad%20targeting%2C%20and%20streamline%20customer%20interactions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChatbots%2C%20predictive%20analytics%2C%20and%20automated%20campaign%20optimisation%20will%20become%20more%20sophisticated%2C%20enhancing%20efficiency%20and%20customer%20engagement.%20Sales%20teams%20will%20integrates%20AI%20capabilities%20into%20its%20marketing%20automation%20platform%2C%20enabling%20predictive%20lead%20scoring%2C%20content%20recommendations%2C%20and%20automated%20email%20marketing%20campaigns%20based%20on%20customer%20behaviour.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThird%2C%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20the%20metaverse%20and%20immersive%20technologies%2C%20CMOs%20will%20explore%20opportunities%20to%20engage%20audiences%20in%20virtual%20and%20augmented%20reality%20experiences.%20Brands%20will%20experiment%20with%20creating%20immersive%20content%20and%20advertising%20within%20these%20virtual%20worlds.%20The%20metaverse%20may%20have%20taken%20a%20step%20back%20last%20year%2C%20but%20is%20expected%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20new%20frontier%20for%20marketing%20in%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11172059%2Fscott-graham-5fNmWej4tAA-unsplash-1-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11172059%2Fscott-graham-5fNmWej4tAA-unsplash-1-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F11172059%2Fscott-graham-5fNmWej4tAA-unsplash-1-1-300x200.j