m%20management%20is%20still%20looking%20at%208-10%20players%20who%20are%20in%20the%20running.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20finalised%20the%2015-member%20squad%20but%20there%20are%208-10%20players%20in%20our%20minds.%20So%20we%20will%20make%20our%20combinations%20according%20to%20the%20conditions.%20In%20the%20West%20Indies%2C%20the%20conditions%20are%20slow%2C%20so%20we'll%20have%20to%20pick%20our%20team%20accordingly.%20As%20far%20as%20Rahul%20Dravid%20and%20I%20are%20concerned%2C%20we've%20tried%20to%20maintain%20clarity.%20We%20try%20to%20tell%20them%20why%20they've%20been%20selected%20or%20not%20been%20selected%20even%20after%20putting%20in%20performances%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20even%20said%20that%20the%20players%20on%20the%20bench%2C%20in%20the%20third%20T20I%2C%20will%20ask%20why%20they%20aren't%20playing%2C%20but%20it%20is%20impossible%20for%20him%20to%20have%20everyone%20satisfied%20and%20happy%20as%20only%2011%20players%20can%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can't%20keep%20everyone%20happy%2C%20that%20is%20what%20I've%20learned%20in%20my%20time%20as%20captain.%20You%20can%20keep%2015%20players%20happy.%20Then%20also%2C%20only%2011%20are%20happy.%20The%20four%20players%20sitting%20on%20the%20bench%20also%20ask%20why%20they're%20not%20playing.%20I've%20learned%20that%20you%20can't%20keep%20everyone%20happy%2C%20and%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20the%20team's%20goal%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Afghanistan%20assignment%20was%20Team%20India's%20last%20before%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20this%20year.%20The%20players'%20selection%20will%20now%20depend%20on%20their%20performances%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705570020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Ftnrlecd8_rohit-sharma-and-virat-kohli-afp_625x300_18_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-afghanistan-t