v.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-student-18-collapses-in-middle-of-coaching-class-in-indore-dies-4885433%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ashok%20Leyland%20to%20make%201225%20buses%20for%20Karnataka%20state%20transport%20undertakings%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705569097000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-08%2F31%2Ffull%2F1661948795-6321.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fashok-leyland-to-make-1225-buses-for-karnataka-state-transport-undertakings-124011800349_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Company%20says%20order%20will%20strengthen%20its%20lead%20in%20Indian%20bus%20manufacturing%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fashok-leyland-to-make-1225-buses-for-karnataka-state-transport-undertakings-124011800349_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fashok-leyland-to-make-1225-buses-for-karnataka-state-transport-undertakings-124011800349_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fashok-leyland-to-make-1225-buses-for-karnataka-state-transport-undertakings-124011800349_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Managing%20Ram%20Temple%20Push%20with%20Five%20Trillion-Dollar%20Economy%20Quest%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20set%20off%20on%20Sunday%20from%20conflict-ridden%20Manipur%20on%20his%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%2C%20a%20two-month%2C%20East-to-West%20political%20journey%20that%20will%20end%20in%20Mumbai.%20Unlike%20the%20first%20phase%20where%20Gandhi%20walked%20from%20Kanyakumari%20in%20the%20South%20to%20Srinagar%20in%20the%20North%20to%20feel%20the%20grassroots%2C%20this%20one%20will%20largely%20be%20on%20wheels.%20He%20will%20demand%20social%2C%20economic%20and%20political%20justice%20for%20people%20and%20also%20reveal%20his%20own%20plan%20to%20deliver%20it%2C%20the%20party%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20roadshow%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20upcoming%20general%20elections%2C%20the%20party%20says%20it%20is%20political%20but%20not%20an%20%26quot%3Belectoral%20rally%26quot%3B.%20That%20is%20as%20true%20as%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%20not%20being%20a%20political%20event%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20elections.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Shri%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Teerth%20Kshetra%20Trust's%20invitation%20to%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20and%20leaders%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20to%20attend%20the%20ceremony%20that%20will%20be%20presided%20over%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20an%20election-eve%20trap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20rejected%20the%20invitation%20saying%20it%20was%20a%20political%20project%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20The%20BJP%20lost%20no%20time%20in%20painting%20the%20rejection%20of%20the%20invite%20as%20an%20affront%20to%20Hindus%2C%20the%20majority%20community%20in%20India.%20The%20Congress%20statement%20said%20that%20Lord%20Ram%20is%20worshipped%20by%20millions%20of%20people%20in%20the%20country%20and%20religion%20is%20a%20personal%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20ally%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party's%20leader%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20made%20the%20same%20point%20with%20elan.%20Yadav%20declined%20the%20invitation%20to%20attend%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20but%20said%20he%20and%20his%20family%20would%20visit%20the%20temple%20later%20as%20devotees%2C%20ensuring%20the%20spotlight%20would%20unwaveringly%20stay%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi's%20reign%2C%20the%20Congress%20ran%20with%20the%20hare%20and%20hunted%20with%20the%20hounds%20on%20the%20mosque-temple%20issue%2C%20but%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20was%20miles%20ahead%20in%20setting%20the%20emotion-tugging%2C%20Hindu%20nationalist%20narrative.%20Ultimately%20the%20Babri%20mosque%20was%20demolished%20under%20the%20Congress'%20watch%20in%201992.%20The%20previous%20year%2C%20the%20party%20had%20presided%20over%20another%20demolition%20where%20the%20Narasimha%20Rao%20government%20smashed%20India's%20socialist%20mould%20of%20economic%20organisation%20and%20governance%20to%20pursue%20a%20free%20markets-driven%20national%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20back-to-back%20events%20created%20the%20opportunity%20for%20two%20compelling%20and%20competing%20political%20narratives%3A%20one%20of%20economic%20development%20and%20another%20of%20religious%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Parivar%20did%20not%20have%20a%20ready%20response%20to%20economic%20liberalisation.%20Within%20months%20of%20Manmohan%20Singh%20throwing%20open%20the%20Indian%20economy%20to%20wider%20private%20and%20foreign%20participation%2C%20the%20Swadeshi%20Jagran%20Manch%20was%20formed.%20It%20was%20the%20first%20Parivar%20organisation%20to%20focus%20on%20broad%20national%20economic%20policy.%20Former%20Sarsanghachalak%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20Madhukar%20Dattatraya%20(Balasaheb)%20Deoras%2C%20who%20was%20the%20principal%20architect%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20movement%2C%20had%20once%20told%20journalists%20that%20the%20Sangh%20never%20really%20gave%20serious%20thought%20to%20economic%20issues.%20Its%20labour%20and%20farmer%20organisations%20were%20narrow-focussed.%20Bereft%20of%20viable%20original%20ideas%2C%20it%20joined%20the%20left%20parties%20to%20oppose%20foreign%20investments%2C%20multinational%20corporations%20and%20computerisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20a%20firm%20grip%20on%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20economic%20development%20narrative.%20The%20country's%20elite%20jumped%20on%20to%20the%20bandwagon%20too%20as%20levies%20fell%20and%20doing%20business%20became%20easier.%20The%20National%20Democratic%20Front%20government%20led%20by%20BJP%20stalwart%20Atal%20Behari%20Vajpayee%20briefly%20managed%20to%20seize%20it%20from%20the%20Congress%20with%20its%20highway%20building%20and%20business-friendly%20policies%20luring%20away%20industrialists%20and%20big%20capital%2C%20local%20and%20foreign.%20Vajpayee%2C%20however%2C%20completely%20misread%20the%20widening%20social%20fissures%20and%20economic%20inequality%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20BJP's%20%26quot%3BIndia%20Shining%26quot%3B%20campaign%20seemed%20like%20a%20slap%20on%20the%20face%20of%20the%20millions%20struggling%20for%20livelihoods.%20Although%20the%20Congress%20wrested%20back%20power%20and%20the%20original%20architect%20of%20liberalisation%20Manmohan%20Singh%20was%20heading%20the%20government%2C%20it%20swung%20the%20other%20way%2C%20alienating%20businesses%20and%20the%20rising%20middle%20class%20of%20the%20country%20for%20its%20welfarist%20bent.%20The%20Parivar%20still%20did%20not%20have%20a%20viable%20answer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%2C%20until%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20then%20Gujarat's%20helmsman%20and%20a%20favourite%20of%20industrialists%2C%20demonstrated%20how%20to%20seamlessly%20combine%20ideology%20with%20big%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20is%20the%20crowning%20glory%20of%20the%20strategy%20of%20merging%20unabashed%20Hindutva%20with%20business%20success.%20According%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20over%20100%20chartered%20planes%20are%20expected%20to%20land%20on%20January%2022.%20The%20city's%20spanking%20new%20international%20airport%20will%20not%20have%20space%20to%20accommodate%20the%20private%20planes%20of%20the%20business%20leaders%20and%20movie%20stars%20arriving%20at%20the%20invitation%20of%20the%20temple%20trust.%20It%20would%20almost%20be%20remiss%20if%20the%20Sensex%20and%20Nifty%20do%20not%20set%20a%20new%20record%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20moment%2C%20the%20Parivar%20has%20control%20over%20the%20narratives%20of%20India's%20economic%20growth%20and%20establishment%20of%20a%20muscular%20Hindu%20nation.%20The%20gathering%20at%20Ayodhya%20will%20be%20testimony%20of%20the%20Indian%20elite's%20buy-in%20into%20the%20Parivar's%20cause.%20But%20just%20like%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20completed%2C%20widespread%20economic%20growth%20is%20also%20a%20work%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20research%20report%20titled%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3E'The%20Rise%20of%20Affluent%20India'%2C%20Wall%20Street%20bank%20Goldman%20Sachs%20said%20only%20about%204%25%20of%20working%20age%20Indians%20had%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20%2410%2C000%20(Rs%208.3%20lakh)%20or%20more.%20It%20converts%20to%20about%2060%20million%20consumers.%20The%20bank%20estimated%20this%20number%20to%20rise%20to%20100%20million%20by%202027%2C%20the%20same%20year%20when%20India%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20third%20largest%20economy%20with%20a%20GDP%20of%20%245%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remaining%201.3%20billion%20have%20a%20long%20wait%20to%20glimpse%20affluence%2C%20which%20Goldman%20measures%20by%20the%20ability%20to%20buy%20premium%20brands%2C%20eat%20out%20often%2C%20and%20spare%20time%20for%20leisure.%20The%20temple%20may%20be%20a%20spiritual%20balm%20for%20a%20large%20section%20of%20the%20majority%20community%2C%20but%20it%20certainly%20does%20not%20help%20put%20bread%20on%20the%20table%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20Indians.%20That%20is%20why%20the%20government%20has%20promised%20free%20food%20for%20five%20years%20to%20813%20million%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20is%20pitching%20himself%20and%20the%20Congress%20Party%20as%20the%20champion%20of%20this%20majority%20with%20his%20yatra.%20Other%20than%20handing%20out%20largesse%20in%20states%20that%20it%20rules%2C%20so%20far%20the%20Congress%20has%20not%20revealed%20any%20viable%20ideas%20to%20wrest%20the%20narrative%20of%20economic%20development%20from%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20writer%20is%20editor%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdaily.thesignal.co%5C%22%3EThe%20Signal%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20author%20of%20The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Making%20Of%20The%20Deep%20Nation.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705569000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F5umh44hg_ayodhya-ram-temple-ani_625x300_17_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmanaging-ram-temple-push-with-five-trillion-dollar-economy-quest-4879299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20is%20the%20crowning%20glory%20of%20the%20strategy%20of%20merging%20unabashed%20Hindutva%20with%20business%20success.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A23%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmanaging-ram-temple-push-with-five-trillion-dollar-economy-quest-4879299%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmanaging-ram-temple-push-with-five-trillion-dollar-economy-quest-4879299%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fmanaging-ram-temple-push-with-five-trillion-dollar-economy-quest-4879299%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Teacher's%20Aide%20Admits%20To%20Having%20Sex%20With%20%26quot%3BNumerous%26quot%3B%20Teenage%20Boys%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20former%20teacher's%20aide%20has%20admitted%20in%20federal%20court%20to%20having%20%26quot%3Bnumerous%26quot%3B%20sexual%20relationships%20with%20teenage%20boys%20while%20working%20at%20an%20elementary%20school%20in%20Kentucky%2C%20US.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F01%2F17%2Fnews%2Fkentu