ion-found-curled-up-next-to-dead-father-4884920%5C%22%3EUK%20Boy%2C%202%2C%20Died%20of%20Starvation%2C%20Found%20Curled%20Up%20Next%20To%20Dead%20Father%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EFox%2056%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20victims'%20mothers%20said%20that%20she%20went%20to%20high%20school%20with%20Phillips%20and%20that%20their%20children%20grew%20up%20together.%20%26quot%3BThese%20boys%20are%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20laws%20that%20protect%20them%20and%20would%20not%20come%20forward%20because%20they%20thought%20they%20would%20be%20in%20trouble%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20son%20reportedly%20told%20her%20that%20the%2038-year-old%20brought%20them%20alcohol%203%20to%204%20times.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20wrap%20my%20mind%20around%20the%20extent%20of%20what%20she's%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEllen%20Phillips%20was%20arrested%20in%20April%202023%20when%20two%20minors%20came%20forward%20and%20said%20she%20had%20raped%20them%20on%20three%20separate%20occasions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20now%20faces%20a%20minimum%20of%2010%20years%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%20life%20in%20prison.%20State%20prosecutors%20will%20consider%20dropping%20charges%20as%20a%20result%20of%20Phillips'%20federal%20guilty%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20U.S.%20Attorney's%20Office%20prosecuted%20this%20case%20as%20part%20of%20Project%20Safe%20Childhood%2C%20a%20nationwide%20initiative%20launched%20in%202006%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20to%20combat%20the%20growing%20epidemic%20of%20child%20sexual%20exploitation%20and%20abuse%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705568880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2F3eb3kf1_us-police-generic_625x300_14_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-teachers-aide-admits-to-having-sex-with-numerous-teenage-boys-4885546%22%2C%