quot%3B%20Aims%20For%20Lunar%20Landing%20To%20Eclipse%20China%20In%20Space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJapan%20aims%20to%20become%20the%20fifth%20country%20to%20put%20a%20spacecraft%20on%20the%20moon%20when%20it%20attempts%20a%20precision%20landing%20on%20Friday%2C%20in%20what%20would%20be%20a%20boost%20for%20a%20space%20programme%20that%20has%20suffered%20a%20wave%20of%20setbacks%20and%20been%20eclipsed%20by%20rival%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDubbed%20the%20%26quot%3Bmoon%20sniper%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Japan%20Aerospace%20Exploration%20Agency%20(JAXA)%20probe%20is%20attempting%20to%20land%20within%20100%20metres%20(328%20feet)%20of%20its%20target%2C%20a%20technology%20JAXA%20says%20is%20unprecedented%20and%20essential%20in%20the%20search%20for%20moon%20water%20and%20human%20habitability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20is%20increasingly%20looking%20to%20play%20a%20bigger%20role%20in%20space%2C%20partnering%20with%20close%20ally%20Washington%20to%20respond%20to%20China's%20military%20and%20technological%20might%2C%20including%20in%20space.%20Japan%20boasts%20a%20number%20of%20private-sector%20space%20startups%20and%20aims%20to%20send%20an%20astronaut%20to%20the%20moon%20as%20part%20of%20NASA's%20Artemis%20programme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20JAXA%20has%20faced%20multiple%20setbacks%2C%20including%20a%20launch%20failure%20in%20March%20of%20the%20new%20flagship%20rocket%20H3%20that%20was%20meant%20to%20match%20cost-competitiveness%20against%20commercial%20rocket%20providers%20like%20SpaceX.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJAXA's%20Smart%20Lander%20for%20Investigating%20Moon%20(SLIM)%20probe%20will%20start%20a%2020-minute%20touchdown%20phase%20on%20its%20one-way%20mission%20from%20midnight%20on%20Saturday%20(1500%20GMT%20Friday)%2C%20trying%20to%20land%20on%20a%20target%20site%20roughly%20the%20size%20of%20two%20athletic%20tracks%20on%20the%20slope%20of%20a%20crater%20just%20south%20of%20the%20lunar%20equator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20other%20nation%20has%20achieved%20this.%20Proving%20Japan%20has%20this%20technology%20would%20bring%20us%20a%20huge%20advantage%20in%20upcoming%20international%20missions%20like%20Artemis%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shinichiro%20Sakai%2C%20JAXA's%20SLIM%20project%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Chandrayaan-3%20in%20August%20made%20a%20historic%20touchdown%20on%20the%20moon's%20south%20pole%2C%20a%20major%20technological%20feat%20given%20the%20rough%20terrain%2C%20highlighting%20India's%20rise%20as%20a%20major%20player%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJAXA%20stresses%20its%20high-precision%20technology%20will%20become%20a%20powerful%20tool%20in%20future%20exploration%20of%20hilly%20moon%20poles%2C%20seen%20as%20a%20potential%20source%20of%20oxygen%2C%20fuel%20and%20water.%20Japan%20also%20plans%20a%20joint%20unmanned%20lunar%20polar%20exploration%20with%20India%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20lunar%20project%20development%2C%20Japan%20can't%20beat%20the%20U.S.%2C%20China%20or%20India%20in%20terms%20of%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kazuto%20Saiki%2C%20a%20Ritsumeikan%20University%20professor%20who%20developed%20SLIM's%20near-infrared%20camera%20that%20will%20analyse%20moon%20rocks%20after%20the%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20focus%20on%20building%20sought-after%20technologies%20like%20the%20pinpoint%20landing%20and%20near-infrared%20cameras%20which%20overseas%20exploration%20projects%20will%20strive%20to%20adopt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJAXA%20has%20twice%20landed%20on%20small%20asteroids%2C%20but%20a%20moon%20landing%20is%20much%20more%20difficult%20due%20to%20its%20gravity%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20a%20number%20of%20recent%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20probe%20belonging%20to%20Japanese%20startup%20ispace%20inc%20crashed%20onto%20the%20moon's%20surface%2C%20and%20Russia's%20Luna%2025%20followed%20suit.%20A%20lander%20from%20American%20startup%20Astrobotic%20last%20week%20suffered%20a%20fuel%20leak%2C%20forcing%20it%20to%20abandon%20a%20touchdown%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMistakes%20happen%2C%20but%20Japan%20is%20a%20very%20experienced%20space%20power%20-%20it's%20conducted%20very%20complicated%20space%20operations%20for%20many%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bleddyn%20Bowen%2C%20a%20University%20of%20Leicester%20associate%20professor%20specialising%20in%20space%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20as%20big%20as%20the%20United%20States%20or%20the%20Soviet%20Union%20of%20old%20or%20China%20today%20in%20terms%20of%20scale%2C%20but%20in%20terms%20of%20capability%20and%20niche%20advanced%20technologies%2C%20Japan%20has%20always%20been%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESLIM's%20precision%20landing%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20be%20a%20game%20changer%26quot%3B%2C%20but%20the%20demonstration%20of%20it%20and%20the%20lightweight%20probe%20manufacturing%20Japan%20has%20pursued%20might%20open%20up%20moonshots%20to%20space%20organisations%20worldwide%20by%20reducing%20the%20cost%20of%20each%20mission%2C%20Bowen%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJAXA%20says%20it%20will%20take%20up%20to%20a%20month%20to%20verify%20whether%20SLIM%20has%20achieved%20the%20high-precision%20goals%20after%20touchdown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20landing%2C%20SLIM%20will%20also%20deploy%20two%20mini-probes%20-%20a%20hopping%20vehicle%20as%20big%20as%20a%20microwave%20oven%20and%20a%20baseball-sized%20wheeled%20rover%20-%20that%20will%20take%20pictures%20of%20the%20spacecraft.%20Tech%20giant%20Sony%20Group%2C%20toymaker%20Tomy%20and%20several%20Japanese%20universities%20jointly%20developed%20the%20robots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(Reporting%20by%20Kantaro%20Komiya%3B%20Additional%20reporting%20by%20Irene%20Wang%3B%20Editing%20by%20David%20Dolan%20and%20Nick%20Macfie)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705568700000%2C%22vi