Over%20Sexual%20Harassment%20Complaint%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F13132528%2FIIM-Calcutta-Auditorium.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%20Calcutta%20(IIM-C)%20has%20removed%20its%20director-in-charge%2C%20Sahadeb%20Sarkar%2C%20because%20of%20an%20allegation%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20against%20him.%20The%20institute%20announced%20this%20decision%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday%20(January%2016).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Internal%20Complaints%20Committee%20(ICC)%20of%20the%20institute%20has%20been%20in%20receipt%20of%20a%20written%20complaint%20under%20the%20Sexual%20Harassment%20of%20Women%20at%20Workplace%20(Prevention%2C%20Prohibition%20and%20Redressal)%20Act%2C%202013%20(POSH%20Act)%20against%20the%20then%20Director-in-Charge%20professor%20Sahadeb%20Sarkar.%20The%20ICC%20has%20ascertained%20that%20prima%20facie%20the%20complaint%20warrants%20a%20formal%20inquiry%20and%20communicated%20the%20same%20to%20the%20Board%20of%20Governors%20(BoG)%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIIM-C%20Board%20of%20Governors%20held%20a%20special%20meeting%20on%206%20January%202024%20and%20accepted%20the%20recommendation%20of%20the%20ICC%20that%20professor%20Sahadeb%20Sarkar%20shall%20not%20continue%20in%20the%20office%20of%20Director-in-Charge%20and%20shall%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20said%20post%20and%20any%20other%20position%20wherein%20he%20has%20administrative%20charges%20in%20IIM%20Calcutta%2C%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20formal%20inquiry%20before%20the%20ICC%20and%20any%20proceedings%20arising%20therefrom%20or%20incidental%20thereto%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Fiim-calcutta-removes-director-over-sexual-harassment-complaint-9112870%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20next%20senior-most%20faculty%20member%2C%20professor%20Saibal%20Chattopadhyay%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20director-in-charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarkar%20is%20the%20third%20IIM%20director%20in%20three%20years%20to%20leave%20before%20his%20term%20is%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarkar%20has%20called%20the%20allegations%20%E2%80%9Cbaseless%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fdirector-in-charge-sahadeb-sarkar-removed-over-sexual-harassment-case-iim-calcutta%2Fcid%2F1994256%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20%E2%80%9CI%20emphatically%20deny%20the%20allegations%20made%20against%20me.%20I%20am%20shocked%20with%20the%20baseless%20allegations.%20In%20any%20case%20this%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20official%20press%20release%20by%20the%20management%20and%20I%20am%20prevented%20from%20speaking%20to%20the%20press%20by%20the%20POSH%20rules%2017(6)%20of%20the%20institute.%20I%20will%20address%20this%20appropriately%20at%20an%20appropriate%20forum%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705553109000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2F13132528%2FIIM-Calcutta-Auditorium.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiim-calcutta-removes-director-sahadeb-sarkar-over-sexual-harassment-complaint%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20next%20senior-most%20faculty%20member%2C%20professor%20Saibal%20Chattopadhyay%2C%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20director-in-charge.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fiim-calcutta-removes-director-sahadeb-sarkar-over-sexual-harassment-complaint%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Prosecutor%20investigating%20Ecuador%20TV%20station%20attack%20shot%20dead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705552440000%2C%22visua